.SH DESCRIPTION
.TP
.BR iswhite ", " isnum ", " range ", " ishex ", " isoctal ", " ISB64CHAR
Macros for character checking like isalnum(3).
.TP
.B top_gethexnum
Function for converting hex numbers from string to integer.
.TP
.BR top_base64decode ", " top_base64encode ", " top_base64encode_short ", " top_base32encode_short
Functions for base 64/32 (en/de)-coding
.TP
.BR top_dos2unix ", " top_unix2dos
Converts text from to dos line termination.
.TP
.BR top_getline ", " top_getfield
Splits text in lines / fields.
.TP
.BR top_findchar ", " top_findstr
Finding characters or strings in strings.
.TP
.BR top_striplncomment ", " top_skipwhite ", " top_skipwhiteplus ", " top_stripwhite
Strips away white spaces or line comments (e.g. everything from # to line end) in strings.
.TP
.B top_delcr
Deletes carrage return characters in texts.
.TP
.BR top_atoi64 ", " top_atou64
String to integer convertion for 64 bit integers.
.TP
.B top_isnum
checks wether a string is a number.
.TP
.B Unicode conversion functions.
The frlib contains a couple of functions for converting between utf8, 
utf16 and utf32.
These functions are:
.BR utf2wchar_char ", "
.BR utf2wchar_str ", "
.BR utf8ucs2_char ", "
.BR utf8ucs2 ", "
.BR utf8ucs4_char ", "
.BR utf8ucs4 ", "
