.BR ucs2utf8_charlen ", "
.BR ucs4utf8 ", "
.BR ucs4utf8_char ", "
.BR ucs4utf8_len ", "
.BR ucs4utf8_charlen
.TP
.BR utf8blen ", " utf8clen ", " utf8tlen
Functions for calculating the string length in utf8 encoded strings.
.TP
.BR utf8bcmp ", " utf8ccmp ", " utf8tcmp ", " utf8lcmp
Functions for comparing two utf8 strings.
.TP
.BR top_lat1utf8 ", " top_utf8lat1
Converts strings between latin1 and utf8.

